{"tid":2417601,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"里亞德錄大地 動畫化決定","createTime":"2021-02-22T04:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T05:13:43.000Z","uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"456592eaca38c737ffaf7f335bc91bf478b4933d","tid":2417601,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:31:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/leadale_anime/status/1363685236261888006?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fleadale_anime%2Fstatus%2F1363685236261888006%3Fs%3D21&d=nAM79WGQOJ1S2Ssbv1FDY0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=cbea13e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fleadale_anime%2Fstatus%2F1363685236261888006%3Fs%3D21&h=ce3501da\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/leadale_anime/status/1363685236261888006?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n由 Ceez 撰寫、てんまそ繪製插畫的輕小說作品《里亞德錄大地（リアデイルの大地にて）》，官方宣布動畫改編的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZT4a5xh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZT4a5xh.jpg&h=296b2f05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《里亞德錄大地》故事描述，由於遭逢意外，身體只能依靠維生系統活著的少女「各務桂菜」，只有在VRMMORPG「里亞德錄」中可以自由活動。然而某一天，她因為維生系統停止而失去生命。但醒來時，她發現這裡是自己玩過的「里亞德錄」的世界&hellip;&hellip;而且是兩百年後的世界！她以高等精靈「葵娜」的身分調查這兩百年間發生了什麼事，同時和活在這世界的人們以及自己創造出來的非玩家角色們交流，然而──<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P60p9Zz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP60p9Zz.jpg&h=7128c602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bebg06e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbebg06e.jpg&h=3b847282&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《里亞德錄大地》是於「成為小說家吧」發跡，目前日版預定將於 2 月底發行第 6 集，台灣則是由角川代理發行，目前預定將於 3 月底發行第 3 集。目前動畫尚未宣布將於何時推出，對於本作有興趣的人，可關注後續相關報導。"},{"pid":"5218d82bccf68516ecebb7db2024633bf6cbd7b4","tid":2417601,"uid":18605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"呢套好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />J哂小說"},{"pid":"5f212ce01c03a99b640a3403f0f363c128a217a7","tid":2417601,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"抄刀劍"},{"pid":"84a348846b111d2d3518158af386dfd045e6ca73","tid":2417601,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f212ce01c03a99b640a3403f0f363c128a217a7","tid":2417601,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"抄刀劍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"刀劍係史詩級經典<br />\n佢的出現影響後世多位作家的創作<br />\n後現代作品好難會撇除到刀劍的影子"},{"pid":"62ed8c5006acadfa444f6ae31c3c8fc26e64ac3c","tid":2417601,"uid":44828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:04:38.000Z","msg":"係咪百合"},{"pid":"f4e723ce326c78698359fd33d1731af8820af377","tid":2417601,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84a348846b111d2d3518158af386dfd045e6ca73","tid":2417601,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f212ce01c03a99b640a3403f0f363c128a217a7","tid":2417601,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"抄刀劍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"刀劍係史詩級經典<br />\n佢的出現影響後世多位作家的創作<br />\n後現代作品好難會撇除到刀劍的影子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:09:43.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c7afb8359ea6b97e0621fb12f9188c3eb00782","tid":2417601,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"84a348846b111d2d3518158af386dfd045e6ca73","tid":2417601,"uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5f212ce01c03a99b640a3403f0f363c128a217a7","tid":2417601,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:32:26.000Z","msg":"抄刀劍"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T04:38:15.000Z","msg":"刀劍係史詩級經典<br />\n佢的出現影響後世多位作家的創作<br />\n後現代作品好難會撇除到刀劍的影子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-22T05:13:43.000Z","msg":"冇錯 有d穿越異世界直